--- v1.2 development series ---

- Make conversation view the default
- Improve the message reader with more actions
- Add the ability to manage contacts (address book integration, gravatar support, etc.)
- More keyboard shortcuts: 'e', 'u', '#'
- Added a link to edit drafts
- More aggressive quote recognition
- Fix appearance on Windows systems
- Fix some strange cases where the conversation view was broken until you
restart Thunderbird, or when messages were almost hidden.
- New pref: only expand the message scrolled to
